   King Broadcasting
   Is Put Up for Sale
   By Major Holders
   ---
   Bullitt Sisters' Plan Is to Use
   Proceeds for Environment
   In the Pacific Northwest
   ----
   By Charles McCoy
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
